configProfile.description:
Here you can create and manage multiple LLM Provider options. You can create separate options for different Models of the same LLM Provider, with each configuration storing complete LLM Provider configuration settings. After configuration, you can quickly switch between different Models at the bottom of the chat input box.

Configuration includes:
 LLM Provider name (e.g., OpenRouter, DeepSeek, Anthropic),
 API Key,
 Model,
 And other provider-specific settings.

Steps to create an option:
1. Select a LLM Provider below;
2. Enter API Key, Model ID, and other information;
3. Only click the + button to create a new dropdown option after entering all required LLM Provider information;
